OL,3,CDesign teams meet with Grenfell
OL,4,Csurvivors for future memorial on site
OL,6,FBereaved families and survivors of the
OL,7,FGrenfell Tower fire are to meet with
OL,8,Fpotential design teams about a future
OL,9,Fmemorial to be built on the site.
OL,11,FAround 28 design teams had applied to
OL,12,Fbe part of the project and a shortlist
OL,13,Fof five has now been announced.
OL,15,FIn what the Grenfell Tower Memorial
OL,16,FCommission described as an "extensive
OL,17,Fsecond round of evaluation", the teams
OL,18,Fwill meet with bereaved, survivors and
OL,19,Fthose living in the surrounding
OL,20,Fcommunity to hear their views.
