OL,6,FSeparate to the commission's work, a
OL,7,Fdecision on the future of the tower
OL,8,Fitself is expected to be made by the
OL,9,FHousing Secretary Angela Rayner in
OL,10,FFebruary.
OL,12,FThe Government has previously said
OL,13,Fthere will be no changes to the site
OL,14,Fbefore the eighth anniversary in June.
OL,16,FThey added that structural engineering
OL,17,Fadvice remained unchanged "in that the
OL,18,Fbuilding (or that part of it that was
OL,19,Fsignificantly damaged) should be
OL,20,Fcarefully taken down".
