OL,6,FWhat is left of the tower has stood in
OL,7,Fplace since the fatal disaster on 14
OL,8,FJune 2017 with a covering on the
OL,9,Fbuilding featuring a large green heart
OL,10,Faccompanied by the words "forever in
OL,11,Four hearts".
OL,13,FThe Government's latest update
OL,14,Fregarding the site acknowledged views
OL,15,Fwithin the community including both
OL,16,Fthat the tower's presence on the
OL,17,Fskyline helps ensure what happened is
OL,18,Fnot forgotten while also being a
OL,19,Fpainful reminder for those who live,
OL,20,Fwork and study nearby.
