OL,6,FThe memorial commission, in a 2023
OL,7,Freport, set out a series of
OL,8,Frecommendations for a "sacred space"
OL,9,Fin the area of the tower, designed to
OL,10,Fbe a "peaceful place for remembering
OL,11,Fand reflecting".
OL,13,FIt said the space should include a
OL,14,Fgarden, a monument and a dedicated
OL,15,Fspace for the private expression of
OL,16,Fgrief and mourning for the families
OL,17,Fwho lost loved ones.
OL,19,FThe winning design team is set to be
OL,20,Fselected in summer.
