OL,6,FThe shortlist includes four UK-based
OL,7,Fteams, namely Curl La Tourelle and
OL,8,FHead Architecture; Freehaus; George
OL,9,FKing Architects and Grow to Know; and
OL,10,FOffice Sian.
OL,12,FThe fifth candidate, New South, is
OL,13,FFrance and Belgium-based and is
OL,14,Fcurrently involved in designing a
OL,15,Freligious and cultural centre in
OL,16,Fcentral Paris.
