OL,6,FIn a joint statement, the memorial
OL,7,Fcommission's 10 community
OL,8,Frepresentatives said: "Having a
OL,9,Fshortlist of teams brings us another
OL,10,Fstep closer to turning the Grenfell
OL,11,Fcommunity's memorial vision into a
OL,12,Fphysical reality.
OL,14,F"Through this process, we intend to
OL,15,Fidentify and appoint a specialist and
OL,16,Fworthy design team.
