OL,6,F"One that has proven experience of
OL,7,Fworking on sensitive and community-
OL,8,Ffocused projects, and who can leave no
OL,9,Fdoubt in our minds about the integrity
OL,10,Fwith which they will approach the
OL,11,Fvital task of designing a beautiful
OL,12,Fand fitting future memorial.
OL,14,F"Our 72 loved ones, and our community,
OL,15,Fdeserve nothing less."
