OL,6,FThe Royal Institute of British
OL,7,FArchitects (Riba), which has helped in
OL,8,Fthe shortlisting process, paid tribute
OL,9,Fto the "number and quality of the
OL,10,Finitial entries and the compassion,
OL,11,Fthoughtfulness and clarity of the
OL,12,Fentrants' desire to undertake this
OL,13,Fimportant community-led commission".
OL,15,FThe commission said it expects the
OL,16,Fmemorial design to be sufficiently
OL,17,Fdeveloped to enable a planning
OL,18,Fapplication to be submitted in late
OL,19,F2026.
